\begin_layout Section*
About Chopstix
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Chopstix is a software program that can be used to improve your business
 by handling the entire order and delivery process from telephone number
 to customer and kitchen receipt.
 Chopstix is designed to simplify your order process, improve your customer
 relationships, and assist in reconciling multiple payment methods tendered
 by your customers.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section*
What's New?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Everything.
 Chopstix has been in production continuously since December 2005, but this
 is the first release available to the public.
 Some highlights include:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Customer database searchable by telephone number that contains not only
 name and address but preserves special instructions between orders.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Order entry from your own menu with real time updates of the order total.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Order database that preserves all posted orders including customer, individual
 items, and special instructions.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Menu system capable of attaching styles, extra items, and sub items for
 combos.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Receipts printed in a two column format that can be split for kitchen and
 customer receipt at order time.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Complaint and Credit system that allows you to handle complaints by applying
 a future order credit to a customer account.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Persistent Special Instructions can be stored by customer and print on all
 current and future orders.
\end_layout

