Creating a new customer is easy, simply enter a new telephone number and
 a new customer detail record is created.
 Just fill out the details and the customer is entered into your database.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The next time the customer orders, simply enter the telephone number and
 all details are retrieved ready to be printed on the receipt.
\end_layout

