 Individual totals are stored for each of subtotal, discount, delivery,
 credit applied, taxes and the total.
 Any customer special instructions are posted with the order to record the
 instructions at the instant orderd.
 Orders can be retrieved in full to present accurate information in case
 of customer dispute or financial audit.
\end_layout

