Order Items
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
An order is constructed from individual order items added to the order.
 Each order line contains a quantity of a single menu item.
 As items are chosen, the order is expanded as required.
 Up to four thousand items may be added to a single order.
 Items are chosen by code from your menu.
